1
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:31,900
[The Dark Romance]

2
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,950
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,220
[Outpatient]

4
00:01:37,220 --> 00:01:38,289
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

5
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,560
I'll prescribe a week's worth
of medication for you.

6
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,690
It's not addictive,

7
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:55,270
so take it without worry.

8
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:00,300
It's fine.

9
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,640
You're my psychiatrist.

10
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:07,270
What gives you the right
to send me to another department?

11
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,560
Li Changning.

12
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,210
You're disrupting my work.

13
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,680
Why did you send me...

14
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,050
to that kind of department?

15
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,329
Because I believe you donated eggs,

16
00:02:19,329 --> 00:02:20,450
being completely irresponsible

17
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:22,380
with your body, just to make money.

18
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:24,280
Those marks on your stomach

19
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,870
were from
ovulation stimulation injections.

20
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:26,630
Be gentle.

21
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,890
And not just once in a short period.

22
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:35,190
I arranged gynecological examinations
and consultations for you

23
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,190
to help determine

24
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,520
whether you'll ever be able

25
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,450
to have children in your lifetime.

26
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,000
Breaking up isn't the end of the world.

27
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:47,780
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

28
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,380
Let me tell you,

29
00:02:45,670 --> 00:02:48,000
a proper ex should be like
he's dead to you.

30
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,710
It's okay to cry on the first day,

31
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,800
but by the second day,
you should delete and block him.

32
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:55,280
By the third day,
eat what you want, have fun,

33
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:58,250
and meet a new boyfriend.

34
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,610
You told me to find a new boyfriend.

35
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,680
You can ignore that part.

36
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,280
Sometimes,

37
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:31,030
being alone is actually quite nice.

38
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,680
As long as one is healthy and happy.

39
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,829
But don't they say

40
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,170
lovers will stay together

41
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,840
forever?

42
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,030
It's my fault.

43
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,710
It's my bad.

44
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:01,540
I lost the love lock necklace he gave me.

45
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:04,080
He said I didn't cherish our relationship.

46
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:05,340
But I did.

47
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:07,800
I really did.

48
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,760
The one who didn't cherish it
certainly wasn't you.

49
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:13,400
He must have known
your financial situation.

50
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,470
You bought him a phone

51
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:15,750
and rented an apartment.

52
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,870
Didn't he ever ask you

53
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:18,329
where the money came from?

54
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,709
After egg retrieval,

55
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,170
one can't have sex for at least 14 days.

56
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,720
Your frequent, unregulated egg donations

57
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,320
have severely damaged
your ovarian function.

58
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,950
And

59
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:35,440
you had
completely unprotected sexual activities.

60
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,360
Your infection is so severe

61
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,770
that I find it hard to believe

62
00:04:39,770 --> 00:04:40,850
he didn't notice.

63
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:44,390
Did he really care about you,

64
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:46,070
Li Changning?

65
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:51,930
So in the future...

66
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,440
So in the future,

67
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,290
will I not be able to have children?

68
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,200
That depends on you.

69
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:04,270
If you follow the doctor's treatment
properly

70
00:05:04,350 --> 00:05:06,480
and don't abuse yourself like before,

71
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:07,940
I believe

72
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,980
you'll still have a chance to be a mother.

73
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,600
You hear that?

74
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,700
What kind of sound is that?

75
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,530
Its foot is injured.

76
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,430
Yes.

77
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,909
Bitten by its boyfriend.

78
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,810
How did this happen?

79
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:44,190
Fortunately,
the store clerk found it in time;

80
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:46,240
otherwise,
it would've been bitten to death.

81
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,500
Hamsters are very territorial animals.

82
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,720
Mothers, their offspring,

83
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:53,190
or even male and female hamsters
after mating

84
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,920
will all fight with each other.

85
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:02,660
Your boyfriend bit you.

86
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,610
You must be very sad.

87
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,180
But it's also very strong.

88
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,720
It quickly came to terms with it.

89
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,030
Not only did it stop feeling sad,

90
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:14,310
but it bit back hard.

91
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,930
It saved itself from death.

92
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:23,620
I bought it home.

93
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,310
But I've been busy lately.

94
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,590
I'm afraid I won't have time
to take good care of it.

95
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:28,630
Could I trouble you

96
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:30,290
to look after it for a few days?

97
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:35,290
By the time its wounds heal,

98
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,760
you should be ready
to leave the hospital.

99
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:52,350
[Police]

100
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:34,810
This little horse
was Godmother's favorite.

101
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,600
She said Godfather gave it to her.

102
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:39,490
Now that Godmother is gone,

103
00:07:39,490 --> 00:07:42,420
Godfather must be even more heartbroken
than we are.

104
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,780
So we'll keep it...

105
00:07:49,350 --> 00:07:50,480
for Godmother.

106
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:17,460
[Cangshan District, Lihai City,
Dongchuan Province]

107
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:17,950
[920 Xiangan Road]
[To Jian Leilei]

108
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:27,780
[Demand Letter]

109
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:36,380
[Demand Letter] [Zirui Finance]

110
00:08:39,770 --> 00:08:47,060
[Demand Letter]

111
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:42,570
No wonder
she misappropriated client funds.

112
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,810
She even mortgaged her house.

113
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:47,790
If the repayment is not completed
within 30 days,

114
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:49,850
the house will be seized for auction.

115
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:54,470
This house meant everything to Leilei.

116
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,740
The day she paid off her mortgage,

117
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:59,410
she even treated Jiale and me to dinner.

118
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:02,050
How could she bear to lose it?

119
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:05,080
Did she trade crypto with leverage?

120
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,840
Because with leverage,

121
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,290
once there are losses,

122
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:10,520
she must meet the margin requirement.

123
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:11,540
Otherwise,

124
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,200
they'll force her
to liquidate her position,

125
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,150
and she'll lose everything.

126
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:16,550
In that case, she might mortgage anything.

127
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:18,210
Do you think this loan company

128
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:20,120
might be connected with

129
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:22,600
the platform
where Leilei lost her investment?

130
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,600
But didn't you check
her investment company?

131
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,750
You said it was legitimate.

132
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,680
Look into this loan company again.

133
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,360
Are you and Jiale

134
00:09:34,450 --> 00:09:35,300
okay now?

135
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,500
We're fine.

136
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,470
Thanks to Dr. Luo.

137
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,120
Dr. Luo?

138
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,600
W-What?

139
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,330
What Dr. Luo?

140
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,500
You don't know him.

141
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,800
He's a psychologist.

142
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,970
You're just using this to look into it?

143
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,360
I've already checked all this.

144
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,290
I came to you because I had no leads.

145
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,940
I thought you had
some special connections.

146
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,340
I-I'm just an ordinary person.

147
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:07,420
It's easy for me
to check the weather forecast.

148
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:10,400
Alright then, I'm leaving.

149
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,870
Aren't you going home yet?

150
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,600
I-I'm working overtime today.

151
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,670
I'm sorry

152
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:15,390
for bothering you.

153
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,190
No, not at all.

154
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:16,670
Oh, right.

155
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,240
Um,

156
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,620
about the money,

157
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,050
if it really needs to be repaid,

158
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,120
I can still provide it.

159
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,030
No, no need.

160
00:10:23,110 --> 00:10:24,640
It's not your place anyway.

161
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,540
I'll think of another way.

162
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,360
I'm leaving now.

163
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,150
Okay, okay.

164
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,710
Don't worry too much.

165
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,550
We found a trunk full of luxury goods

166
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:01,440
in Jian Leilei's car trunk.

167
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:03,080
They're roughly estimated

168
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,850
to be worth nearly one million.

169
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:07,080
Only her fingerprints were on the box.

170
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,080
I'm sorry, Ma'am.

171
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:14,690
Our store can't accept these items.

172
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,000
Why?

173
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,600
We can't verify their authenticity.

174
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,830
I have receipts for all of these.

175
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:29,200
Counterfeiting is rampant
in the luxury market now.

176
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:29,960
Many fake products

177
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,390
can be indistinguishable
from the real ones.

178
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,360
They even have

179
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,240
complete packages including invoices,

180
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,750
full packaging,

181
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,870
and even credit card receipts.

182
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,400
These most valuable items—

183
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:39,200
these bags,

184
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,670
this diamond watch, and this bracelet—

185
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:43,960
are all counterfeits
after our verification.

186
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,910
Counterfeits?

187
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:48,480
Only official boutique purchases
are authentic-guaranteed.

188
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,880
Other channels, like personal shoppers,

189
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,030
might sell fakes.

190
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,660
What about this little horse?

191
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,090
Xia Yi.

192
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,790
Sorry.

193
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:13,370
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

194
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:15,140
Please try again later.

195
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:19,530
It's also fake.

196
00:12:23,930 --> 00:12:26,070
[Premium Pawnshop]

197
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:32,250
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

198
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,860
Please try again later.

199
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,320
[Police Reminder] [No Fighting]
[Losers in Hospital; Winners in Jail]

200
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:39,920
Officer Li.

201
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,320
Ms. Yan.

202
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:45,690
What is it?

203
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:48,820
[Police]

204
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:48,670
Xia Yi said he was with you that day.

205
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:50,240
He said you had a good chat.

206
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,120
Is that right?

207
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:51,910
Yes.

208
00:12:52,770 --> 00:12:54,670
He had just returned
from a rescue mission.

209
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:56,320
After seeing you, he went to the hospital

210
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,530
to visit Leilei's parents.

211
00:12:57,530 --> 00:12:58,720
Seeing who? Me?

212
00:12:59,390 --> 00:13:00,600
We never met.

213
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:03,550
Well.

214
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,360
He called and said

215
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,080
he received our voicemail

216
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,150
and asked what it was about.

217
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:11,010
I explained the situation to him.

218
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,080
He knew Jian Leilei's mother
was in the hospital,

219
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,270
so he said he'd find you first

220
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,790
and asked if he could give his statement
after returning.

221
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:16,920
I said that was fine.

222
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,860
But what did he say after that?

223
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:20,200
Went...

224
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:20,720
Went where?

225
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,320
Minzhou.

226
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,030
He said there was a fishing boat accident
in Minzhou.

227
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,630
His rescue team
needed to go provide support.

228
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,360
So I told him to handle his business first

229
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,200
and deal with this when he gets back.

230
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,730
This matter wasn't urgent.

231
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:31,270
You didn't even see him in person,

232
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:32,400
and you just agreed?

233
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:34,840
How can you be a police officer?

234
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,640
What kind of police work is this?

235
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:39,140
You completely neglected your duty!

236
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:39,840
Wait.

237
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:41,960
Ms. Yan.

238
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,840
We rely on evidence in our investigations.

239
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:45,320
Right?

240
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,270
Jian Leilei committed suicide
out of guilt.

241
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:48,030
The evidence is complete,

242
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:48,840
and the chain is clear.

243
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,030
As far as this case is concerned,

244
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,760
there's no problem closing it.

245
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,600
Her financial transactions with Xia Yi

246
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,030
show nothing suspicious.

247
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,490
I've checked everything.

248
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:58,250
They're not even married.

249
00:13:58,610 --> 00:14:00,790
I asked him to come just to cooperate
with our investigation

250
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:01,990
and give a statement.

251
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,980
He's not a criminal suspect. I...

252
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:05,460
Then why did Xia Yi lie to me

253
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,990
about having met you?

254
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:09,960
He lied about this.

255
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:10,960
How can you be sure

256
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,890
he hasn't lied about other things?

257
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:14,510
His phone is unreachable.

258
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,030
The gifts he gave to Leilei are fake.

259
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,090
His car was rented.

260
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:19,200
We don't even have a single photo of him.

261
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,360
Isn't that strange?

262
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,000
I'll investigate anything suspicious,

263
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:22,480
okay?

264
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,550
I understand how you feel right now.

265
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,440
But you can't let your emotions

266
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,360
lead you to criticize our law enforcement—

267
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,960
I'm not criticizing law enforcement.

268
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,160
I'm criticizing you.

269
00:14:33,190 --> 00:14:33,930
Uncle.

270
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:36,030
Did Leilei ever mention

271
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,830
what Xia Yi's company is called?

272
00:14:39,930 --> 00:14:40,660
No.

273
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:44,240
I heard Xia Yi often sent you
health supplements.

274
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,520
Do you still have any of the packaging

275
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,790
or delivery tracking numbers

276
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:48,840
from those packages?

277
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,300
They were all bought by Xia

278
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:52,290
and sent to us through Leilei.

279
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:55,010
When Xia Yi and Leilei
visited your hometown,

280
00:14:55,010 --> 00:14:56,870
did you take any photos together?

281
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,660
What's wrong? Did something happen?

282
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:03,200
Nothing. It's nothing.

283
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:06,390
I just want to gather everything

284
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:07,470
related to Leilei.

285
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,450
As a keepsake, you know.

286
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,270
Thank you for your thoughtfulness.

287
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:13,530
But we didn't get a chance to take photos.

288
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:15,180
They came on the weekend

289
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,930
in such a rush,

290
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:19,030
and stayed for just one day and left.

291
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:21,710
Okay, that's all, Uncle.

292
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:22,770
I'll hang up now.

293
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:32,860
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

294
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,670
Xia Yi.

295
00:15:35,970 --> 00:15:39,590
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

296
00:15:37,270 --> 00:15:38,960
Two women, one old man,

297
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,080
and one in prison.

298
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,590
That's all.

299
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:43,840
Fatty, is Chief Hu's speech ready yet?

300
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:44,750
[China Police]

301
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,870
Hurry up. He's asking for it.

302
00:15:44,870 --> 00:15:45,970
Working on it, working on it.

303
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:46,510
[China Police]

304
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:51,660
Jerk.

305
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,680
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

306
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:53,890
He even dared to lie to the police.

307
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:55,610
Chief Hu.

308
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:02,950
What are you doing?

309
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,600
Who told you to investigate this?

310
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,600
Stop it right now.

311
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,490
Explain yourself clearly.

312
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:13,090
Master.

313
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:14,900
This is important.

314
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,440
I strongly suspect

315
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:17,830
that Xia Yi

316
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:19,110
used a fake identity.

317
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,670
I just checked our system,

318
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,630
and nothing matches up.

319
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:24,510
And also,

320
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:26,980
he bought his phone number from a dealer.

321
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,150
He used it for half a year

322
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:30,410
to almost exclusively call Jian Leilei.

323
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,240
The ID card he used to rent the car

324
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,030
wasn't even his own.

325
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,120
He used an employee's.

326
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:34,550
Don't you think

327
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:35,790
we should investigate him

328
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:37,720
since he was extremely deliberate

329
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,600
about hiding his true information?

330
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,800
What do you say, Master? What do you say?

331
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:46,670
I've searched the Business Database.

332
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:49,530
There's no company
associated with the name Xia Yi.

333
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,150
And on the blacklist of dishonest persons,

334
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:53,010
this name doesn't appear either.

335
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:56,610
I've checked again

336
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:59,290
through all my chat history with Leilei.

337
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,930
She never sent me any photos of Xia Yi.

338
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:04,780
I couldn't reach his phone.

339
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:07,020
I don't have a single photo of him.

340
00:17:07,510 --> 00:17:09,839
Isn't this like he vanished into thin air?

341
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:12,460
Maybe we're overthinking this.

342
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,750
If there really is something wrong,

343
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:16,550
the police wouldn't just
sit around doing nothing.

344
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:17,920
Don't mention the police to me.

345
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:20,140
I met a kid who barely has facial hair.

346
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,690
He knew absolutely nothing

347
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:24,579
and still talked to me
with that bureaucratic tone.

348
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:27,660
Yan Jiale.

349
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,600
You've come out 5 times already.

350
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,380
What do you want this time?

351
00:17:32,430 --> 00:17:34,160
You already have a girlfriend.

352
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:36,240
Why are you still here to see my mom?

353
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:39,350
What nonsense are you talking about?

354
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:41,510
Your father and I are discussing
important matters.

355
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:42,910
What important matters?

356
00:17:43,310 --> 00:17:44,310
By the way, Jiale,

357
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,860
when you used to go out
with your godparents,

358
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:50,230
what kinds of things would you do?

359
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,350
Well,

360
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:53,410
movies, meals, things like that.

361
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:55,980
Besides eating and watching movies,

362
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,740
what else would you do?

363
00:17:58,160 --> 00:18:00,360
Last time we went to the hot springs...

364
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,770
Godfather went too.

365
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:03,920
He's really professional at swimming.

366
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:06,720
He has a very long scar here.

367
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:09,190
He said he got cut
by a sunken ship's anchor

368
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:10,720
during a rescue operation.

369
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,970
Did you take any photos of them?

370
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,560
You never bought me a phone,

371
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:16,210
so how could I take photos?

372
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:18,110
What an excuse.

373
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,680
What else?

374
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,640
Godfather is really good at gaming.

375
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:25,240
He even helped me rank up before.

376
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,550
Gaming?

377
00:18:27,370 --> 00:18:28,080
This is it.

378
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:29,100
[Fly Fashion Is Here] [Start Now]

379
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:29,540
[Start]

380
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:31,640
You have this skin already?

381
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:33,910
[Social] [Team]

382
00:18:33,930 --> 00:18:34,570
[Friends]

383
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:37,910
What's wrong?

384
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,420
Godfather deleted his account.

385
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,790
[User Deleted]

386
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,200
Most people who stop playing

387
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,600
would just leave their accounts inactive.

388
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:48,170
Nobody would actually
delete their account.

389
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:52,940
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

390
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,580
[Model Collective
for Homicide Case Detection]

391
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:09,240
[Technical Department]

392
00:19:15,390 --> 00:19:19,200
[Confidentiality System]

393
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:17,210
Ms. Sun.

394
00:19:17,250 --> 00:19:19,340
I heard you like these little things,

395
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:20,710
so I brought you one.

396
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:24,400
I-I also brought you some snacks, Ms. Sun.

397
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:25,820
Well, these things I brought

398
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:27,980
are all delicious,
but won't make you gain weight.

399
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:29,450
They'll leave you speechless, Ms. Sun.

400
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:32,620
[Confidentiality System]

401
00:19:29,470 --> 00:19:31,000
-Don't give me that.
-Have a taste.

402
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,680
I'm old enough to be your mother.

403
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,740
So disrespectful.

404
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:35,840
You're just joking.

405
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:38,030
You're so young.

406
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:39,510
How could you be my mother?

407
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,880
Even calling you "Ms."
makes you sound too old.

408
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:41,380
See?

409
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,730
Try it. It's really delicious.

410
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:44,550
Ms. Sun.

411
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,690
Case filing first for a sketch.

412
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:56,950
Ms. Sun,

413
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,500
can you do me this small favor?

414
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,160
Just

415
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:01,200
draw it first.

416
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,330
Besides, even if...

417
00:20:02,590 --> 00:20:03,820
I mean, even if

418
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,120
I do you this favor

419
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:06,790
and draw this sketch,

420
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:08,960
you'd still need your eyewitness

421
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,400
to provide an accurate enough description.

422
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,160
Accurate. Definitely accurate.

423
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,560
Ms. Sun, she's a teacher.

424
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:15,000
A university professor.

425
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,400
She has excellent verbal skills,

426
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,160
-insulting people without dirty words.
-No matter how accurate she is,

427
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:20,160
there would still be room
for error in my hearing and understanding.

428
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,240
There would be no error.

429
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,750
How could you possibly make mistakes?

430
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:23,160
That's ridiculous.

431
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,160
Don't change the subject.

432
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:24,890
Listen to me.

433
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,500
A composite sketch

434
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:30,020
is drawn based on verbal descriptions.

435
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:32,150
The describer's mouth and my ears

436
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:33,440
aren't cameras.

437
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:35,070
It's impossible to recreate

438
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:36,790
the subject's appearance
with 100% accuracy.

439
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:37,720
Even at its best,

440
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:40,720
there's at least a 15% margin of error.

441
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,440
Let me put it this way.

442
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:49,350
If you use a composite sketch
for in-person comparison,

443
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:50,550
it might be useful.

444
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:52,550
Because there's such a thing
as resemblance.

445
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:54,680
But if you give the sketch

446
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,640
to a computer

447
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,750
for facial recognition,

448
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:58,110
the machine's algorithm

449
00:20:58,110 --> 00:21:00,370
doesn't have an option for resemblance.

450
00:21:07,310 --> 00:21:08,590
But I just want to know

451
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:09,080
what he

452
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,070
actually looks like.

453
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:15,720
Even though you use this sketch I draw

454
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:18,160
to compare with photos
in the household registration system,

455
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,960
do you have time
to sift through tens of thousands

456
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:22,550
or even hundreds of thousands of photos,
like finding a needle in a haystack?

457
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:24,310
You'd be better off thinking of other ways

458
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,510
to find other leads.

459
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:35,770
[Rent across Miles, Service within Smiles]

460
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:35,880
Dong A 4728K is a Land Rover.

461
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,890
I called to confirm at the time.

462
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:39,440
He rented the car from here.

463
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,590
We've already checked the system.

464
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,270
-There really isn't Xia Yi.
-Ma'am.

465
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:44,400
You're the one who reported us, right?

466
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,070
The police have already fined us.

467
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:47,270
What more do you want?

468
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,030
The police?

469
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,110
I've already explained everything

470
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,480
to Officer Li.

471
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,400
I don't know that person

472
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,530
called Xia Yi at all.

473
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,840
He just gave me some extra money

474
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:58,590
to use my ID card
for the car rental procedure.

475
00:21:58,590 --> 00:21:59,270
He returned the car on time,

476
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,870
and there were no accidents.

477
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:04,000
You shouldn't have called the police,
should you?

478
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:07,590
I'm sorry.

479
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,080
Hello?

480
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:20,510
I logged into Jiale's gaming account

481
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,160
and checked his battle records.

482
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,500
For a while,

483
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:24,000
he

484
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,880
often played with the person
using this avatar.

485
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,680
I suspect this person was Xia Yi.

486
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,550
I'll send you the picture

487
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,850
of his avatar first.

488
00:22:34,550 --> 00:22:35,440
Octopus.

489
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:55,350
No!

490
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,240
Zhang.

491
00:23:02,750 --> 00:23:04,810
Could you help me with the paperwork?

492
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:06,590
Going to Gangdao again?

493
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,160
Yes.

494
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:08,790
They are all old patients I met

495
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:09,880
during my internship.

496
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:10,880
We've fraternized.

497
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,930
I won't rest easy unless they're attended.

498
00:23:12,930 --> 00:23:14,240
Thank you for your help.

499
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:14,840
Oh, right,

500
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,070
Li Changning's condition

501
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:18,000
has become much better these days.

502
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,930
Her mother even jokes with us now.

503
00:23:20,350 --> 00:23:20,810
Really?

504
00:23:25,370 --> 00:23:30,300
[Fantian Tattoo]

505
00:23:27,510 --> 00:23:28,790
I have a drawing here.

506
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,880
Those surrounding the eye

507
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,540
should be octopus tentacles.

508
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:34,960
If you recall anyone who got this tattoo,

509
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,680
will you please let me know?

510
00:23:36,850 --> 00:23:42,900
[Fantian Tattoo]

511
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:37,550
Chen.

512
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,720
Did any client ask for this tattoo?

513
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,320
This is...

514
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:42,880
"the Eye of Medusa."

515
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,020
No one asked for it.

516
00:23:45,520 --> 00:23:48,550
Then why were the snakes around
changed to octopus tentacles?

517
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:49,280
So messed up.

518
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:51,590
Thanks for your help.

519
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:52,250
No problem.

520
00:23:53,890 --> 00:23:57,000
[Police]

521
00:23:55,110 --> 00:23:55,590
Wei.

522
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:57,920
Where have you gone?

523
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,450
I haven't seen you for days.

524
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,810
I've been on field duty.

525
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:02,550
A hit-and-run suspect fled back

526
00:24:02,550 --> 00:24:04,270
to his hometown in the Northwest.

527
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,680
Dong and I just arrested him

528
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,750
and are now escorting him back.

529
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:07,640
A few days ago,

530
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:10,400
I sent you Xia Yi's profile.

531
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,070
Have you read it?

532
00:24:11,070 --> 00:24:11,480
Who?

533
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,440
Xia Yi.

534
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,130
Oh, that man.

535
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:17,270
No one has asked
to file a report or open a case about him.

536
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:18,400
What do you want me to look into?

537
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,160
Well, look,

538
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:19,960
if you're busy,

539
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,690
my colleague

540
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,890
and I will do the legwork, alright?

541
00:24:23,310 --> 00:24:24,710
Okay. I'm hanging up now.

542
00:24:27,420 --> 00:24:31,160
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

543
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:30,510
Jian Leilei was transferred
to the VIP Service Dept.

544
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:31,240
not long ago.

545
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,070
Here are

546
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,720
the sign-in sheets
for the client events she attended

547
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:34,590
in the past few months.

548
00:24:34,590 --> 00:24:37,680
Most of the these activities
were wine tastings for our VIPs.

549
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,310
I didn't find the name "Xia Yi"

550
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:40,440
that you mentioned.

551
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:41,470
[Sign-in Sheet]

552
00:24:41,330 --> 00:24:44,130
Were there surveillance cameras
in these events?

553
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,090
No.

554
00:24:45,350 --> 00:24:46,720
Premium clients usually care a lot

555
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,920
about their privacy.

556
00:24:48,050 --> 00:24:50,360
[Zhou Xinsheng] [Jiang Gang] [Chen Fei]

557
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:50,610
Does this refer to the richest man

558
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,550
of the city, Zhou Xinsheng?

559
00:24:53,310 --> 00:24:54,160
Yes, it's him.

560
00:24:57,970 --> 00:24:59,800
[Zhou Xinsheng]

561
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:01,570
[Followed!]

562
00:25:05,090 --> 00:25:06,710
[Fine wine warms the heart;
Glad to be in the wine tasting]

563
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:08,930
[and charity auction
held by Lihai Commercial Bank]

564
00:25:06,860 --> 00:25:10,720
A charity auction with wine tasting
held by Lihai Commercial Bank...

565
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,060
Jian Leilei was indeed there.

566
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:21,660
[Hello, Mr. Zhou, may I ask...]

567
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:24,680
[Tattoo Entrance]

568
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:29,750
Hello.

569
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:32,560
Are you the owner of this place?

570
00:25:32,830 --> 00:25:33,200
Yes.

571
00:25:33,310 --> 00:25:33,790
Well,

572
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,500
I have an inquiry.

573
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:38,160
Have you done a tattoo like this?

574
00:25:38,810 --> 00:25:40,400
It's an eye surrounded

575
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,480
by octopus tentacles,

576
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,740
as this picture shows.

577
00:25:49,130 --> 00:25:54,660
[Tattoo Entrance]

578
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:56,480
The patterns we do
are usually original designs.

579
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:58,680
This one...

580
00:25:58,700 --> 00:26:00,700
is not that good. I've never seen it.

581
00:26:01,170 --> 00:26:05,580
[Tattoo services, customized designs]

582
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:06,680
Donkey,

583
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:07,870
this is Chubby Li.

584
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:09,590
Why don't you keep this drawing?

585
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:11,050
If you think of something,

586
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:12,550
please call me.

587
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:13,830
My number is right here.

588
00:26:13,830 --> 00:26:14,480
Okay.

589
00:26:47,170 --> 00:26:50,650
[Clinic]

590
00:26:51,670 --> 00:26:53,330
The paperwork for a leave of absence
has been done.

591
00:26:53,330 --> 00:26:54,160
Let Changning

592
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:55,490
take a good rest at home.

593
00:26:55,610 --> 00:26:56,810
I've also picked some

594
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:58,550
easy-to-read textbooks for her.

595
00:26:58,550 --> 00:27:00,550
She can do some reading in her spare time.

596
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:02,300
Thank you so much, Ms. Yan.

597
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:03,480
Please carefully observe any change

598
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:05,720
in Changning's emotional state
when you're home.

599
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:06,900
If she behaves

600
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,480
differently than usual,

601
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:08,920
call me

602
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,400
or contact Dr. Luo.

603
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,580
Thank you very much.

604
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:14,170
Sorry for all the trouble
our family has caused you.

605
00:27:14,170 --> 00:27:15,030
Don't say that.

606
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:16,680
Changning's well-being

607
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:17,720
matters more than anything.

608
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,120
Right.

609
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,140
Have you done packing?

610
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:28,610
Almost.

611
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,000
Here are the discharge papers.

612
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,640
Okay.

613
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:33,610
Dr. Luo didn't come to work today?

614
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:36,350
He's gone to Gangdao
on a business trip today.

615
00:27:36,350 --> 00:27:37,160
That's why he finished

616
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:39,750
all the checkups
for the discharge yesterday.

617
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:41,070
Do you need to see him about something?

618
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:42,240
I can pass a message for you.

619
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,160
No, nothing.

620
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,840
I just want to thank him in person again.

621
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:48,790
Well, let me know if you need anything.

622
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:49,440
Thanks.

623
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,240
Thank you.

624
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:51,920
Alright. Put it in here.

625
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:53,940
Thank you so much.

626
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,310
Is everything packed?

627
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:57,130
Almost.

628
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,500
Anything left behind?

629
00:27:58,640 --> 00:27:59,670
Ms. Yan.

630
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:01,640
Dr. Luo said

631
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,840
you'd probably come.

632
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,640
He asked me to give this
to you for your son—

633
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:08,240
he needs someone to look after it
for a few days.

634
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:09,790
Okay.

635
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,500
Be careful with its right leg.

636
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:13,810
It was injured before.

637
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,350
Dr. Luo fixed it.

638
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:21,730
Changning,

639
00:28:22,580 --> 00:28:24,040
get some good rest at home.

640
00:28:24,670 --> 00:28:25,930
Listen to your mother.

641
00:28:32,410 --> 00:28:33,960
[Hang Seng Bank]

642
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:37,960
[Gangdao]

643
00:29:13,170 --> 00:29:14,010
Dr. Luo,

644
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,240
thank you so much

645
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:17,400
for taking the time to visit them.

646
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,310
This is what I should do.

647
00:29:18,310 --> 00:29:19,110
Sam asked,

648
00:29:19,130 --> 00:29:20,480
"where is Dr. Luo?"

649
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:21,680
He really misses you.

650
00:29:21,690 --> 00:29:22,190
Does he?

651
00:29:22,210 --> 00:29:22,940
Yes, he does.

652
00:29:23,270 --> 00:29:24,330
Sam is right there.

653
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,420
There you are, Dr. Luo.

654
00:29:26,650 --> 00:29:27,510
Hello, Dr. Luo.

655
00:29:27,590 --> 00:29:28,070
Long time no see.

656
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:28,590
Indeed.

657
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,550
Hello!

658
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:32,640
Sam.

659
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,440
How have you been?

660
00:29:38,670 --> 00:29:39,590
You look good.

661
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:44,790
Shan,

662
00:29:45,170 --> 00:29:47,030
Dr. Luo is here to visit you again.

663
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:53,310
Shan's emotional state
is much more stable now.

664
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:55,040
Nothing unusual has happened.

665
00:29:58,560 --> 00:30:00,960
I don't think I saw this behavior
last time.

666
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:01,590
Really?

667
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:03,310
She's been doing this a lot lately.

668
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:03,870
Yes.

669
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:10,200
Sam.

670
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:12,960
May I?

671
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,550
Thank you.

672
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:48,040
I thought it was a sign of improvement.

673
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:02,260
[Jiale told you not to worry, Dr. Luo]

674
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:03,880
[He'll take good care of the hamster]

675
00:32:12,110 --> 00:32:12,560
Hello,

676
00:32:12,650 --> 00:32:13,580
is it Ms. Yan?

677
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:16,300
I've seen the tattoo you asked about.

678
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:18,800
A fellow tattoo artist

679
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,310
did this pattern for a client

680
00:32:20,310 --> 00:32:21,570
and posted it on Weibo.

681
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:22,730
Take a look.

682
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:26,080
"Dream Traveler"?

683
00:32:30,290 --> 00:32:32,690
[Developed by Traveler Quadrant]
[Founder: Liu Ping]

684
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,060
[Founder: Liu Ping]

685
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,610
Mr. Yan,

686
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,880
you said it all right.

687
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:47,680
It's true that the client has

688
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,070
s-some negative reviews now.

689
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:50,160
But they're mainly focused on

690
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:52,050
two parts of the action choreography.

691
00:32:52,050 --> 00:32:53,050
Don't worry.

692
00:32:53,350 --> 00:32:55,350
The design of new characters
and the scene modeling

693
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,680
are already in progress.

694
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,180
With sufficient funds,

695
00:32:58,360 --> 00:33:00,350
the quality is guaranteed to be ushered
to a new level.

696
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:00,880
Mr. Liu.

697
00:33:01,790 --> 00:33:02,350
Mr. Yan,

698
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:03,400
please give me a second chance.

699
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:03,760
I...

700
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:04,800
Hello? Hello?

701
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,220
Lyu.

702
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:08,440
Listen up, Lyu.

703
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,070
What the heck is this?

704
00:33:10,070 --> 00:33:12,440
My money is used for quality improvement.

705
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:14,680
I'm not here to be ripped off
by these ungrateful people.

706
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:15,640
What garbage is this?

707
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:16,480
What is this trash?

708
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,350
Hurry, get out!

709
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:18,250
Yes, yes.

710
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:20,400
What's wrong with you all?

711
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:27,750
What's up?

712
00:33:27,750 --> 00:33:28,400
I'm sorry, Mr. Liu.

713
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,110
She insists on meeting you.

714
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:30,270
What am I paying you guys for?

715
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:31,240
Why haven't you driven her away?

716
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:31,840
I'm sorry.

717
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,550
Mr. Liu is having a conference!

718
00:33:33,550 --> 00:33:34,270
Sorry, Mr. Liu.

719
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:35,640
I really need to confirm

720
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,680
something important with you.

721
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:37,830
It's related to a human life.

722
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:39,820
-Can we just have a brief meeting?
-Sorry.

723
00:33:39,820 --> 00:33:42,880
-Are you listening, Mr. Liu?
-You really can't do this.

724
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,450
Mr. Liu?

725
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,070
I've never heard of this Jian Leilei

726
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:48,030
you mentioned.

727
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:50,270
Then why did you two go get

728
00:33:50,270 --> 00:33:51,200
the same tattoo?

729
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:53,680
What's so odd about it?

730
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:56,140
P-Patterns alike
are all over the internet.

731
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:57,340
I'd like to know

732
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,240
where you got this drawing.

733
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,220
Also,

734
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:02,230
why did you change—

735
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,680
Medusa's snakes,

736
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:04,200
into

737
00:34:04,350 --> 00:34:05,680
octopus tentacles too?

738
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,400
Wait. S-Snakes?

739
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,270
What snakes?

740
00:34:07,270 --> 00:34:08,230
What octopus tentacles?

741
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,960
I don't understand a word you said.

742
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,030
And that girl Jian Leilei,

743
00:34:11,030 --> 00:34:13,070
who you're talking about
—I don't know her at all.

744
00:34:13,070 --> 00:34:15,280
To address any doubts you may have,
call the police!

745
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,630
Stop messing with me!

746
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:19,320
Mr. Liu,

747
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,440
before my good friend Jian Leilei
passed away,

748
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:23,670
she mortgaged her property.

749
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,870
Nobody knows where that money has gone.

750
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:28,800
What I'm going to say

751
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,060
may sound rough to you.

752
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:33,250
I watched the latest financial news.

753
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,760
Recently, your company

754
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:35,320
happens to

755
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:37,230
be facing financial difficulties.

756
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:37,920
Shut up!

757
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:39,880
What's going on?

758
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,130
What are you doing here, Kexin?

759
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:44,230
My apologies.

760
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:44,860
Sorry.

761
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:47,510
Why did you throw a temper tantrum again?

762
00:34:47,510 --> 00:34:48,070
No, I didn't.

763
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:50,130
Just ignore this woman. She's crazy.

764
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:52,730
How could you talk to others this way?

765
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:56,639
I'm sorry. He has a bad temper.

766
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,030
Why aren't you leaving?

767
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,360
I'll call the security.

768
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:02,120
It didn't scare you, did it?

769
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:05,300
Who is she?

770
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:07,110
I don't know her at all.

771
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:10,860
What's the result
of the obstetric checkup?

772
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,800
Very fine.

773
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:12,340
Really?

774
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:31,310
[A game developed by my husband]

775
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:33,900
[Xin, be bright and happy]

776
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,620
Why not come upstairs?

777
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:50,230
You have a girlfriend now.

778
00:35:50,230 --> 00:35:52,000
Going to your place too often
is inappropriate.

779
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,040
It's okay.

780
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,120
If you want to...

781
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:56,160
Well, we can talk here.

782
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:57,840
What happened?

783
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,110
I came here to tell you

784
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,480
that I have

785
00:36:00,590 --> 00:36:02,840
found out
who has the same tattoo as Leilei.

786
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,510
Let me see.

787
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,150
He's the owner of a gaming company,

788
00:36:06,150 --> 00:36:06,960
named Liu Ping.

789
00:36:06,510 --> 00:36:08,420
[Save the picture]

790
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,940
He's kind of a public figure.

791
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:11,590
Did he tell you

792
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:14,450
why the snakes were replaced
by octopus tentacles?

793
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:14,970
No.

794
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,590
You need to tell the police about it,
right?

795
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,580
But before that,

796
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,880
I should at least prove
he was acquainted with Leilei,

797
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,880
or that they had some sort of connection.

798
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:25,940
Well, these days,

799
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,960
he's in urgent need of money.

800
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,430
His financial situation is terrible.

801
00:36:30,430 --> 00:36:31,690
He's already married.

802
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,480
I found his wife's Weibo account. Look.

803
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:36,240
[Picking up my husband from work—
not just a daily routine]

804
00:36:36,090 --> 00:36:37,600
She seems rich and pretty.

805
00:36:36,260 --> 00:36:37,790
[But also a way to express
and convey affection]

806
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:38,830
He's short of money,

807
00:36:38,830 --> 00:36:40,430
and his wife is very wealthy.

808
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:41,110
Well,

809
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,190
so he's targeting

810
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:44,510
rich women like her for money then?

811
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:47,000
I-Is it correct?

812
00:36:49,070 --> 00:36:49,960
Ms. Yan, look.

813
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,840
Is Xia Yi in these photos?

814
00:37:01,660 --> 00:37:06,050
[Officer Li]
[Xia Yi is not in any of these photos]

815
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,360
My work-out is done.

816
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,440
I'll be home soon.

817
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:13,840
Okay.

818
00:37:14,550 --> 00:37:15,110
Hello.

819
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:18,820
You must be Mr. Liu's wife, right?

820
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,480
Are you that lady I met

821
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,190
in my husband's office that day?

822
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,190
Yes, I am.

823
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,360
Can I have a word with you?

824
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:30,110
How do you know my husband has a tattoo?

825
00:37:30,590 --> 00:37:32,030
What's your relationship with him?

826
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:33,690
No, please don't get me wrong.

827
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,320
I'm a college teacher.

828
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,320
My surname is Yan.

829
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:38,840
My good friend

830
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,320
had the same tattoo

831
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:43,460
as your husband.

832
00:37:44,030 --> 00:37:46,090
She committed suicide some time ago.

833
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:48,690
Before that,
she had taken out a huge loan.

834
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,810
Why would she commit suicide?

835
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,970
What a poor thing.

836
00:37:55,670 --> 00:37:56,990
Do you know

837
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:58,670
what that tattoo stands for?

838
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:02,160
That's all in the past.

839
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,730
Liu Ping and I are married now.

840
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:07,440
Everything in the past is behind us.

841
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,320
I read your Weibo posts.

842
00:38:12,710 --> 00:38:15,180
You seem to be from a wealthy family.

843
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,620
What are you implying?

844
00:38:18,030 --> 00:38:18,880
Has Liu Ping

